txt.en: 'Why would you allow this to happen? These are Abominations!'
'We must save the Altered People. Speak with me to save them.'
'This is not a simple decision. Save the Altered People.'
'Speak with me, [placeholder]. We must not kill any more.'
'Do not listen to Blaire. Killing them will solve nothing!'
'Do not listen to this woman. Stop the threat of Saruman.'
'End this nightmare now! We must finish what you started!'
'Killing these Abominations is the only way!'
'Why save that which is already lost?'
